 class=\"song_buy_icons compact_buy_icons transition3 clearfix mobile_visibility_hide\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-407c93b all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"407c93b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-1\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Introduction<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8820442 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8820442\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In today&#8217;s dynamic digital landscape, businesses are more focused than ever on providing exceptional customer experiences (CX). Amidst the sea of options available to consumers, a seamless and tailored CX can differentiate brands, fostering loyalty and driving revenue. At the heart of this transformation, leading the charge, are Service <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/process-consultation-documentation\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Cloud Consulting Services<\/strong><\/a>. These services, rooted in the principles of cloud-based customer service and cloud strategy consulting, represent a paradigm shift in how organizations interact with and serve their customers.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The narrative of business-customer relationships has always been underscored by the quality of experiences delivered. With the rise of digital channels, this narrative has only intensified. In fact, according to a recent study by <\/span><b>Smart Karrot<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, over <\/span><b>89%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> of companies now believe they compete primarily based on CX. Another compelling statistic from <\/span><b>Smart Karrot<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> suggests that improving customer experiences is the top priority for about 73% of businesses.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c0f628 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0c0f628\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-2\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">The Evolution of Customer Experience<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7898f76 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7898f76\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tracing back the roots, the emphasis on customer satisfaction is hardly new. Brick-and-mortar establishments, in their heyday, relied heavily on interpersonal interactions, ensuring each patron felt valued. However, with the digital revolution, this dynamic saw a drastic change. Brands were no longer just competing on products or prices; they were competing on the entirety of a customer&#8217;s digital journey.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The transition to digital brought with it a deluge of data. Every click, every page view, and every abandoned cart offered insights. This data-centric approach prompted businesses to refine their strategies, leveraging technology to offer more personalized and efficient customer experiences. Yet, with this shift came challenges. The traditional tools that once sufficed became obsolete in the face of these digital demands.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The solution? A shift towards cloud-based customer service platforms. According to <\/span><b>WebFx<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, companies utilizing cloud-based CRM systems saw an average increase of <\/span><b>74%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in customer satisfaction. This evolution wasn&#8217;t just about technology; it was a fusion of technology with strategy, data, and human touch. This combination set the stage for the rise of Service Cloud platforms.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The revolution wasn&#8217;t just technological; it was strategic. Brands started to understand the importance of a holistic approach, with cloud strategy consulting becoming a key component of this paradigm. With an array of tools and technologies flooding the market, it became essential to choose the right ones that aligned with a brand&#8217;s specific needs and goals. Enter: cloud consulting, poised to guide businesses through this intricate maze.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the following sections, we&#8217;ll delve deeper into the world of Service Cloud platforms, exploring their functionalities, advantages, and the undeniable role of consulting in optimizing their implementation.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4e7e3a0 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4e7e3a0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-3\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Unpacking Service Cloud Platforms<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4176004 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4176004\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ever thought of service cloud platforms as customer service superheroes? Well, Service Cloud platforms are sort of like that. They&#8217;re here to shake things up and change the whole game of how businesses chat and vibe with their customers. With this nifty cloud magic, businesses can flexibly grow, switch gears as needed, and robustly handle all those online chit-chats, making every digital handshake count.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-079a7e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"079a7e7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Unpacking-Service-Cloud-Platforms-qwfn9c4q1nzmtqll7ujj997sbpdoy48xzto17wslyo.jpg\" title=\"Unpacking Service Cloud Platforms\" alt=\"Unpacking Service Cloud Platforms\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-95a0a2d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"95a0a2d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, at the heart of these platforms, we&#8217;ve got these cloud-based CRM systems, right? Think of them as the unsung heroes, the MVPs, of customer relationship management. Now, get this: MarketWebBetter did some digging and found out a whopping 82% of businesses are jumping on this cloud-CRM bandwagon to seriously up their customer experience game. From keeping tabs on customer details to playing fortune teller with predictive analytics, these tools are giving businesses the full movie of a customer&#8217;s journey. This means they can fine-tune every interaction and make customers feel like rockstars.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yet, the sheer power of these platforms can be overwhelming. With countless features and functionalities, the task of optimizing them for one&#8217;s unique business needs becomes daunting. This is where <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/blog\/the-role-of-a-marketo-consulting-company-in-enhancing-marketing-roi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>cloud strategy consulting<\/strong><\/a> steps in, bridging the gap between technology and strategic implementation.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d7325e all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8d7325e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-4\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">  The Indispensable Role of Cloud Consulting Services<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae22c1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ae22c1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cloud consulting has emerged as a pivotal player in this landscape. Their expertise lies not just in understanding the technical intricacies of Service Cloud platforms but in molding them to align with a business&#8217;s strategic objectives. Essentially, they are the architects, ensuring the technology serves the brand&#8217;s larger goal of enhancing customer experiences.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A recent report by <\/span><b>Exploding Topics<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> highlighted that companies leveraging cloud consulting services saw an average increase of <\/span><b>84%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in customer retention rates. This underscores the vital role these consultants play in guiding businesses through the complexities of the cloud landscape.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Additionally, cloud consulting services bring a wealth of insights on best practices and trends. With the pace at which technology evolves, staying updated becomes a herculean task. These consultants, with their fingers on the pulse of the industry, ensure businesses remain at the forefront of innovation. For instance, a survey by <\/span><b>Salesforce<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> revealed that <\/span><b>77%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> of businesses feel better equipped to handle technological changes post-engagement with a cloud consulting service.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, the journey to improved customer service doesn&#8217;t end at mere implementation. Continuous optimization, regular training, and staying updated with evolving trends are crucial. This ongoing partnership with cloud services ensures businesses are always a step ahead, ready to meet their customers&#8217; ever-evolving expectations.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the subsequent sections, we&#8217;ll further delve into the tangible benefits businesses have witnessed with the integration of Service Cloud platforms and how they&#8217;re shaping the future of customer experiences.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-835e62e all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"835e62e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-5\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Tangible Benefits of Integrating Service Cloud Platforms<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c65bcc6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c65bcc6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It&#8217;s no random trend that businesses are hopping onto the cloud-based customer service train and doubling down on cloud consulting. And why&#8217;s that? Because they&#8217;re seeing real, hands-on perks. We&#8217;re talking smoother operations and customers wearing bigger smiles. Everyone&#8217;s a winner!<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a1945a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"4a1945a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Tangible-Benefits-of-Integrating-Service-Cloud-Platforms-qwfn9xr0eut88rq6plvyclrdzkf4v5mrqso799wjzk.jpg\" title=\"Tangible Benefits of Integrating Service Cloud Platforms\" alt=\"Tangible Benefits of Integrating Service Cloud Platforms\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33365ef elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"33365ef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">First off, the whole &#8220;scale up or scale down&#8221; thing with cloud-based CRM systems? Absolute game-changer. Businesses can flex according to their needs, and there&#8217;s no more nail-biting over infrastructure limits. And get this: a recent study showed that a cool <\/span><b>56%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> of businesses felt they could stretch their wings even more after bringing Service Cloud platforms into the mix. How&#8217;s that for room to grow?<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Moreover, the real-time analytics provided by these platforms empowers businesses to understand customer behaviors and preferences like never before.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lastly, in today&#8217;s digital era where customer expectations are continually evolving, cloud strategy consulting enables businesses to stay agile. The guidance from experts ensures that businesses not only implement the best tools but also utilize them in the most optimal way. A study by <\/span><b>CloudZero <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">that businesses leveraging cloud consulting witnessed a <\/span><b>29%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> improvement in customer feedback and reviews.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f00f82d all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f00f82d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-6\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">  Future Outlook: The Evolving Landscape of Customer Service<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-88e0088 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"88e0088\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As the digital landscape continues to evolve, so do customer expectations. Cloud-based customer service tools and cloud consulting services are not mere trends but essential components for any forward-thinking business.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An interesting projection by <\/span><b>Cloud Management Insider<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> suggests that <\/span><b>85%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> of all customer interactions will be managed without a human agent, emphasizing the role of automated, cloud-based solutions. This paints a picture of a future where Service Cloud platforms, augmented by AI and machine learning, become the primary touchpoints for customers.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Moreover, the importance of personalized experiences is only going to grow. With data-driven insights from cloud-based CRM systems, businesses will be better equipped to deliver tailor-made experiences. A report from<\/span><b> Destination CRM<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> underlined this, stating that <\/span><b>80%<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> of customers are more likely to engage with a brand if offered personalized experiences.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In conclusion, cloud strategy consulting and the rise of Service Cloud platforms signal a paradigm shift in the realm of customer service. While technology will continue to play a central role, the real differentiator will be how businesses leverage this technology to foster genuine, lasting relationships with their customers.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f3da52f all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f3da52f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-7\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">The Imperative Shift to Cloud-Centric Customer Service<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8dda4de elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8dda4de\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In the evolving digital landscape, the increasing importance of delivering seamless, effective, and personalized customer experiences cannot be overstated. Businesses are swiftly recognizing this and making the decisive move towards cloud-based customer service platforms and consulting services. This strategic shift isn&#8217;t a mere trend\u2014it&#8217;s an imperative adaptation for modern businesses to not only thrive but to set themselves apart in a competitive market.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Service Cloud platforms, in their essence, empower businesses to elevate their customer service game. With the arsenal of real-time analytics, scalability, and AI-driven automation they bring to the table, these platforms are reshaping the way businesses interact with and serve their customers. The benefits are multifold, ranging from heightened operational efficiency to enriched customer relationships. The numbers back this assertion. Researches from reputed sources like Forrester Research, Adobe Digital Insights, and MarketingProfs have quantitatively demonstrated the tangible positive impacts of these integrations.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yet, as with all technological solutions, the efficacy isn&#8217;t just in the adoption but in the adept implementation and utilization. This is where cloud strategy consulting comes into play. Leveraging the expertise of cloud consulting services ensures that businesses aren&#8217;t merely using a tool, but they&#8217;re using it optimally, staying agile and adaptive in the face of evolving customer expectations and technological advancements.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Peering into the future, it&#8217;s evident that the trajectory points towards a more automated, AI-driven customer service paradigm. While technology will be at the forefront, the human touch cannot be discounted. The fusion of these platforms with empathetic human interaction will be the gold standard of customer service. Cloud consulting, with their expertise, will play an instrumental role in guiding businesses towards this harmonious blend, ensuring that technology serves its purpose of enhancing human connections, not replacing them.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To stay competitive, businesses must continually adapt, and in the realm of customer service, the path forward is crystal clear: a strategic shift towards Service Cloud platforms, augmented by expert cloud consulting services.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For organizations keen on embarking on this transformative journey, or for those looking to optimize their current cloud strategy, the first step is often the most crucial. Seeking guidance, understanding best practices, and charting out a strategic roadmap is imperative. For this, conversations with experts in the domain can be invaluable.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Interested in delving deeper into how Service Cloud Consulting can bolster your customer service strategy? Let&#8217;s take this conversation forward. Click below to schedule a meeting with our <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">cloud strategy experts<\/a> and embark on a journey towards customer service excellence.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-3c33351\" data-id=\"3c33351\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-0286dea elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"0286dea\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;],&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-e210c1b\" data-id=\"e210c1b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c5af724 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c5af724\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Latest WhitePaper<\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8288614 elementor-grid-1 elementor-grid-tablet-2 elementor-grid-mobile-1 elementor-posts--thumbnail-top elementor-posts__hover-gradient elementor-widget elementor-widget-posts\" data-id=\"8288614\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;cards_columns&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;cards_row_gap&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:5,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;cards_columns_tablet&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;cards_columns_mobile&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;cards_row_gap_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;cards_row_gap_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"posts.cards\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-posts-container elementor-posts elementor-posts--skin-cards elementor-grid\" role=\"list\">\n\t\t\t\t<article class=\"elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-22071 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail category-white-papers\" role=\"listitem\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__card\">\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-post__thumbnail__link\" href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/white-papers\/ai-powered-operations-organizational-growth\/\" tabindex=\"-1\" ><div class=\"elementor-post__thumbnail\"><img alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" heigh